title: Ranking the NFL's Top 10 (post-draft) Offenses (Football 5/6)
description:
After all the offseason moves, which team is left with the best offense? Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to detail not just the best, but the Top 10 in the league right now. It's hard to supplant the Super Bowl champion Chiefs, but could the Ravens, Saints or Cowboys pull it off? You might be surprised with some teams that cracked the list as well...
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
